cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a new implementation of Kohonen self-organising maps (SOM) to dissimilarity matrices, which is a common technique in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of SOM in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Additionally, the use of branch and bound principle is a common optimization technique in neural networks (cs.NE).
